full_text: Screened by NARA, 7/13/2023 November 20, 1987 TO WHOM IT MAY CONCERN: I, ADOLFO ESTRADA, of legal age, being duly sworn depose and say that I have known Ms. MEDARDA VALERIO LAMBERT for over 50 years. Also, I further state that since she arrived in the United States over 5 years ago I have seen her constantly. If you desire any more information, please notify me. ADOLFO ESTRADA 75 West 119 St. New York, N.Y. 10026 Tel. 966 7964 State of New York ) County of New York Subscribed and sworn to before the 20 of November 1987. me this Notar day MARLEY NUNE Doming York ile pire New You 6167829 April Brenx 30, Co. Co, 1988
